mated system to simulate attacks with the latest phishing, ransomware, identity theft and malware techniques.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>MDR &#8211; Managed Detection and Response:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> A whole technological stack, processes and trained people with great expertise, who are working 24\/7 to detect and respond to any event. How does it achieve this?\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With prevention: monitoring, management of security policies throughout the network and endpoints.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With automatic detection: threat intelligence and behavioral analysis based on Machine Learning, with enriched data.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With investigation: root cause analysis and timeline analysis.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With response: construction and use of playbooks, automation tools, interconnected platforms and professional experts in the technology stack.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Those responsible for the cyber-attack are making extortive charges to the company to decrypt the files.\u00a0 Information and customer databases of the Municipal Companies of Cali have been endangered, due to the infection of the commercial system equipment with a malicious virus. It entered through a computer that is part of an interconnected network that &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/msiamericas.com\/industrial-cybersecurity-startup-claroty-raises-140m-in-pre-ipo-funding-round-3\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Malicious virus infected Emcali&#8217;s servers and customers&#8217; computers.<\/span> Read More &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":16454,"comment_status":"closed